{"tid":701933,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)大叔既愛:沒巨乳 得巨根OK?","createTime":"2018-06-14T13:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T16:01:51.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b5871b158e24e0cc9128bdb91f612dd841b83ec7","tid":701933,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T13:16:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=lWNmadnI4Ab5oPcz7c8hgAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4555e645\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=lWNmadnI4Ab5oPcz7c8hgAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d36aabdc\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=lWNmadnI4Ab5oPcz7c8hgAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=be51b041\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/11/Ossan's_Love_post.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F11%2FOssan%27s_Love_post.png&h=a7b9bb93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n33歲、單身、渴望戀愛與結婚的春田創一（田中圭飾演），某日意外發現上司黑澤武藏部長（吉田鋼太郎飾演）的手機裡，竟大量存有偷拍他的相片，眼見東窗事發，黑澤便直接向春田告白。春田的母親當初為了追尋自我而搬往川越市，正巧後輩長谷川幸也（落合扶樹飾演）正在尋覓住處，於是長谷川便搬到春田家與他成為室友。當自認是異性戀的春田苦惱該如何應對黑澤部長時，同樣暗戀他的長谷川也在此時表露心意，這令春田手足無措，黑澤部長和長谷川也展開了激烈的競爭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=lWNmadnI4Ab5oPcz7c8hgAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=a084ab49\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=lWNmadnI4Ab5oPcz7c8hgAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=16bdd1f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd27f641c2db1fa710f62c3e0bae119665e077b3","tid":701933,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T13:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://shucreem.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/20180425.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshucreem.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F20180425.png&h=1600764f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6b5f9a8f73a170118a188a1d32e841c21b0deae","tid":701933,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T13:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf857864264d6c71cffc7d5b1b51641c9b9547e","tid":701933,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3e221ae682074908e504d1c8aea8